message.body: Landed safely, splurged on a cab to get me to the early bus early. What time should i meet you at blue cat tonight?
Oh that's great! I'm working 3:30-10ish, but I have to swing home around 3 to take the dogs out so maybe Ill see you then.
My bus is running late, ill come in around 9 to see you at el gato azul
See you then. The girls went out and ate dinner already.
